yingyinNormal.zh: 有意思。如果我把寝宫移到了对门，那我回来这里需不需要敲门呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Buchanan residence. May I speak to Mrs. Buchanan? It's Mr. Carraway, her cousin. Madame is not available, Monsieur Carraway.
yingyinNormal.zh: 布坎南宅邸。我找布坎南夫人，我是卡罗威先生，她的表弟。夫人她没空，卡罗威先生。
